    </h2>

    <div class="mb-4 print:hidden">
      <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer p-3 rounded-lg border border-dashed border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50">
        <input type="checkbox" id="counterToggle" class="w-4 h-4 rounded text-blue-600" onchange="toggleSection('counterSection', this.checked)" />
        <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Include counter / perimeter task lighting</span>
      </label>
      <div id="counterSection" class="hidden mt-3 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-3">Position task lights 24 inches from the wall and centered over the counter, not along the perimeter wall itself.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Total Counter Length</label>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="number" id="counter_len_ft" placeholder="12" min="0" max="100"
                class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 shrink-0">ft</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Add all counter sections together</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Task Fixture Lumens</label>
            <select id="task_lumens"
              class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">
              <option value="650">650 lm — standard</option>
              <option value="750" selected>750 lm — bright</option>
              <option value="1000">1000 lm — high output</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-5 print:hidden">
      <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer p-3 rounded-lg border border-dashed border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50">
        <input type="checkbox" id="islandToggle" class="w-4 h-4 rounded text-blue-600" onchange="toggleSection('islandSection', this.checked)" />
        <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Include kitchen island task lighting</span>
      </label>
      <div id="islandSection" class="hidden mt-3 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-3">Island lights are typically spaced every 24-36 inches along the island length, centered over the work surface.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Island Length</label>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="number" id="island_len_ft" placeholder="4" min="0" max="20"
                class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" />
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 shrink-0">ft</span>
              <input type="number" id="island_len_in" placeholder="0" min="0" max="11"
